comments: Adams (OKC) maintains verticality as he defends Barnes' (SAC) driving shot attempt.
Bjelica (SAC) places his hand momentarily on Gallinari's (OKC) hip while moving and removes it without affecting his FOM.
Gallinari (OKC) is already in Joseph's (SAC) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Joseph (SAC) makes marginal contact with Paul's (OKC) arm after Paul has released his driving shot attempt.

Replay review of the foul called on Bogdanovic (SAC) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Bogdanovic (SAC) moves forward and delivers contact to Gallinari's (OKC) front and dislodges him from his rebounding position.
Adams (OKC) and Giles III (SAC) briefly engage and disengage during rebounding.
Schroder (OKC) is moving alongside Joseph's (SAC) path and maintains a legal guarding position as he defends the drive.
Adams (OKC) makes marginal contact with Giles III (SAC) as Giles III is starting his upward shooting motion.
Hield (SAC) cleanly deflects the ball away from Schroder (OKC).
Schroder (OKC) and Hield (SAC) make incidental contact with one another as they attempt to secure the loose ball.
Joseph (SAC) cleanly deflects the ball away from Paul (OKC).
Joseph (SAC) places his hand momentarily on Paul's (OKC) hip and removes it.
Bogdanovic (SAC) and Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
Schroder (OKC) makes marginal contact with Barnes (SAC), and Barnes is able to move through the contact on the play at the basket.
Hield (SAC) commits a take foul on Paul (OKC).
Hield (SAC) makes incidental contact with Schroder's (OKC) arm after he has released his jump shot attempt.
